q(x) & \tilde{r}\left(  x\right)
\end{array}
\right)  .,f_{1}\left(  \lambda\right)  :=\dfrac{a_{1}\left(  \lambda\right)
}{a_{2}\left(  \lambda\right)  },f_{2}\left(  \lambda\right)  :=\dfrac
